2014-08-14  James Gallagher  <jgallagher@opendap.org>

	Removed the old caching stuff
	D    dispatch/BESCache.cc
	D    dispatch/BESCache.h
	M    dispatch/BESReturnManager.cc
	M    dispatch/BESReturnManager.h
